codex
Implemented the reviewer cleanup change in [shellExecutionService.ts](/tmp/refactor-eq-workdir/bb-merged-24763/packages/core/src/services/shellExecutionService.ts).

Changed both execution paths to keep `cmdCleanup` visible to their catch handlers, invoke it during error teardown, and immediately clear the reference after each `cmdCleanup?.();` call. I also added the same immediate clearing after the existing lifecycle cleanup calls so later `exit`/`onExit` events cannot invoke it again.

No tests run, per “Source edits only.”
